 cdAccordion - jQuery plugin for accordion navigations
 
 Examples:
        $("#mylist").cdAccordion();

        $("#mylist").cdAccordion({
                        expandDuration:    200,
                        collapseDuration:  800
                    });

        In the examples above, #mylist is the id of a html ul element.
        
 Options and default values:
        expandDelay:        300
        collapseDelay:      200
        expandDuration:     600
        collapseDuration:   600
        indentMin:          "0px"
        indentMax:          "7px"
        indentDuration:     200
        indentEasing:       "linear"
        unindentDuration:   200
        unindentEasing:     "linear"
        activeClass:        "active"
 
